title: CA Landslide, Shaq's Tinder, Mr. Private Parts, Mexican Thong and more.

description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! We need you, thank you and will continue to deliver. Shirley was being a hater and got called out. Howard Stern had some choice words for those who are against COVID-19 vaccination. Big Dog gives us his thoughts about what happened in NY. The Diesel's Tinder profile didn't even last more than two pumps and a grind. The numbers told the truth about the return of NFL action! Was there a blond black man sighting in Cancun? The landslide in Cali favored GN. Today the show ends with Steve explaining the future and Shirley having the last word.
